name: BMRI-DaRIS
body:
### Welcome to the BMRI-DaRIS code repo.
This repo hosts code used by the Brain & Mind Research Institute at the University of Sydney, Australia. The code compiles to produce a package compatible with the Mediaflux & DaRIS products, released by Arcitecta and the University of Melbourne respectively.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
